txt.en: Since the Whitshaws fell under the sway of Núrzum's forces, wolves roam in great numbers, hunting the game that should feed the people of Wildermore.
Since the Whitshaws fell under the sway of Núrzum's forces, wolves roam in great numbers, hunting the game that should feed the people of Wildermore.
You have defeated a number of wolves in the Whitshaws, but they will return, as long as the unnatural winter holds fast.\n\nAs long as wolves roam, hunters are needed.
